taxonomy: Bags, Wallets and Luggage/Wallets/Men's/Glance Brown Mens Wallet
review: The packing was rock solid as always . 5 stars to that as well as delivery. The item is very good and genuine, its a gift for my dad and he loves it. Thank u Amazon for the genuineness and building faith in your beloved customers!!
The Wallet is very big to fit into the Pocket and looks very bulky.
The Credit Card slots thats given are not even fit for the regular credit Cards.  I have bought it in lightning deals, But have to return it because of this reason.

The wallet build is good. The leather feels good. The color was as shown in picture. The only negative point is that a few card slots are a tight fit. Even then I think with some use it will loosen up. Lot of pockets to manage your stuff. Came in a good package. Thanks Amazon.
Great wallet..leather extremely good..value for money.

I bought this item recently a week ago. Chosen after reading the reviwes...yea purse us good even my husband liked it..But i wil give one star because the leather in the folding side now Itself started going. Even inside also its going..i wanted to replace this But it shows item unavailable..i m nt sure it happend with everyone..for us its True and am really disappointed Bcz it was a Brday gift :'(
Nice leather wallet recommended to others
Very nice quality of leather ;worth to buy this product and will definitely recommend to others, overall very good wallet,and I am fully satisfied.
excellent product inner and outer material is superb packaging is also nice delivered on time by amazon......
